document_data.History:
In the {{YearlinkName|1357}}, not long after [[Manshoon]] stormed out of a meeting on [[Mirtul 21]],{{cite book/The Forgotten Realms Atlas|105}} the High Imperceptor of Bane called on Laelar to pursue capture of [[Shandril Shessair]], a ''[[spellfire]]'' wielder.{{cite book/Spellfire/Paperback 1988|160|10}}

He spearheaded a raid on the [[Twisted Tower]] within [[Shadowdale]] in [[Kythorn 10]], in which he tried to kidnap Shandril. He was foiled by [[Torm (adventurer)|Torm]], [[Rathan Thentraver]], and [[Sharantyr]]. After the battle, Rathan suggested he be kept alive for questioning.

He did not return immediately from the mission.{{cite book/Spellfire/Paperback 1988|185-186|10}}
